So, the best thing to do here is change your Summoner name for your account that's already in JP! The accounts wouldn't overlap either way, but it would force you to change your Summoner name on the account you're transferring over! So what it boils down too is which account do you want to have that Summoner name.  This will also give a run down on how [transfers work](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751924) :) 

If you have any other questions make sure to reach out to me and I will help you! 
